<title>mlky yạ mlky</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̹lhy mlkk ạ̹bdy .. wʿẓym ạsmk fy ạljbrwt
 qdạmk thrb ʿdạk .. wyṣyr lynạ ạlmlkwt
 ạlqrạr- mlky yạ mlky .. qdạmk nṭrḥ tyjạn
