 lmạ m ạlmwt btnạdyh .. yḥyạ wḥạlh ytbdl
 4- mạfysẖ zy ʿml ạ̹ydyk .. wlạ fyh zyk ạ̹lh
 hạqḍy ḥyạty bạsjd lyk .. ạ̹nt ạlʿạly wạ̹nt ạllh</lyrics>
